2026-05-15T02:17:57.4847639Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-15T02:17:57.4848451Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-15T02:17:57.4849259Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-15T02:17:57.4850072Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-15T02:17:57.4850858Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-15T02:17:57.4851606Z 32        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-15T02:17:57.4852190Z 33    -->
