2026-05-15T02:17:57.8847836Z 51    <!--
2026-05-15T02:17:57.8848192Z 52        Foreground service used to keep the Pomodoro countdown alive when
2026-05-15T02:17:57.8848539Z 53        the app is backgrounded. Without this, a viewModelScope coroutine
2026-05-15T02:17:57.8848877Z 54        is cancelled as soon as the user switches apps and the completion
2026-05-15T02:17:57.8849387Z 55        notification is never shown. The timer is declared as a
2026-05-15T02:17:57.8849776Z 56        mediaPlayback foreground service because Samsung One UI suppresses
